---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kelas Bahasa Arab Online">
<main>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-xl mb-xl">
<div class="flex-1 space-y-md text-center lg:text-left">
<span class="text-tertiary font-label-md text-label-md bg-tertiary-fixed px-sm py-xs rounded-full">Program Unggulan TSL</span>
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg text-primary leading-tight">Kelas Bahasa Arab Online TSL</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">Belajar bahasa Arab dari nol secara bertahap dengan bimbingan asatidzah yang amanah dan kurikulum yang terarah.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-sm pt-sm justify-center lg:justify-start">
<button class="bg-[#ea580c] text-white px-xl py-md rounded-full font-title-lg text-title-lg shadow-md hover:brightness-110 active:scale-95 transition-all">Daftar Kelas Bahasa Arab</button>
<button class="border border-primary text-primary px-xl py-md rounded-full font-title-lg text-title-lg hover:bg-surface-container-low active:scale-95 transition-all">Konsultasi Program</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full relative">
<div class="aspect-square bg-secondary-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-outline-variant">
<img alt="Arabic Learning Illustration" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A faceless illustration of a student in a bright modern home office, studying Arabic calligraphy from a laptop screen showing clean digital lessons. The room is filled with soft morning light, featuring a minimalist desk with a stack of books and a plant. The overall aesthetic is clean, academic, and warm, using a palette of soft greens and neutral tones consistent with a professional learning environment." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDHC9cr42GhhvNKbtiban0rXr8XSkI-IyQsiQzFAby94pK5xWvXMmNg_W0BBb6KvHA1vF4S8KVicEBe0PwcSGv_w7ZGCvwC_dVlEZ6W3wocib0xltD8uaROw8zzqRRI-XIHKv4gv26odvIUq_NvtreP4gCXzM_fsWJBCdTLZMdq9or2mNyw-sggqMG0ccYnf4d2bPkn3wzRyG5-uG-JcoJWQuMEBc6vSj7oGb3yVZ-nsnD-JPx54YRhHvnVwcxKG0Do-Bk5Q3kIy6wS">
</div>
<!-- Floating Card -->
<div class="absolute -bottom-xs -left-xs bg-white p-md rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant flex items-center gap-sm">
<div class="w-xs h-xs bg-tertiary rounded-full"></div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface">Pendaftaran Batch 12 Sedang Dibuka</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Positioning / Journey Section -->
<section class="py-xl border-y border-outline-variant mb-xl">
<div class="text-center mb-lg">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary">Bertahap &amp; Terarah</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Kurikulum dirancang untuk membimbing Anda dari tingkat pemula hingga mandiri.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-md relative">
<!-- Journey Item 1 -->
<div class="bg-white p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-xs z-10">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-xs">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">01</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Pemula 1</h3>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Pengenalan huruf, makhraj, dan kosakata harian dasar.</p>
</div>
<!-- Journey Item 2 -->
<div class="bg-white p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-xs z-10">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-xs">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">02</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Pemula 2</h3>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Struktur kalimat sederhana dan percakapan praktis.</p>
</div>
<!-- Journey Item 3 -->
<div class="bg-white p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-xs z-10">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-xs">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">03</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Dasar Lanjutan</h3>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Mulai memasuki kaidah Nahwu dan Shorof dasar.</p>
</div>
<!-- Journey Item 4 -->
<div class="bg-white p-md rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-xs z-10">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-xs">
<span class="text-on-tertiary-container font-bold">04</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Menengah</h3>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Kemampuan membaca kitab dan pemahaman teks kompleks.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Bento Grid: Metode Belajar -->
<section class="mb-xl">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary text-center mb-lg">Metode Belajar Modern</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-md">
<!-- Feature 1: Zoom -->
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-low p-xl rounded-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-lg border border-outline-variant">
<div class="flex-1 space-y-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="video_call">video_call</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md">Interaktif via Zoom</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Sesi tatap muka daring dengan asatidzah berkompeten. Anda bisa langsung bertanya dan berlatih makhraj serta hiwar (percakapan).</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full aspect-video bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant">
<img alt="Online Class Zoom" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A high-quality minimalist visual representation of an online learning interface on a laptop. The screen shows a clean video conference grid with faceless participants and an instructor pointing to Arabic text on a digital whiteboard. The setting is a serene, sunlit room with a soft green and cream color palette, emphasizing focus, technology, and a modern academic atmosphere." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAYZc62zK-wirdJ-xdh8h1mfXAM-OeSt5uu0eEaLQwln7mgJtjFKOuxIMuYMK7rYs30vsRG-_1f9ktmjyfo1jjFAFenTCsT7kn1aKlNRQRu0bR_7iKdT0cUe5soau68QP1pwCCQ_aIQUzTtFGmF2JNVlaGcggTaoxePX9Obx2lyA7gub_APDPx9YkwWL77DH_0CPoiJh5lF6GmysLNpGvzN8pc-kNLodyGQAUtXpFFnO4XYqEPKGkSheAIwhLMFQighIrR-TSufhwvD">
</div>
</div>
<!-- Feature 2: LMS -->
<div class="bg-primary text-on-primary p-xl rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between border border-primary-container">
<div class="space-y-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl" data-icon="dashboard">dashboard</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-primary-container">LMS Terintegrasi</h3>
<p class="font-label-md text-label-md">Akses materi rekaman, modul PDF, dan ujian di satu tempat kapan saja.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-lg pt-md border-t border-primary-container">
<div class="flex items-center gap-xs">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-label-sm text-label-sm">Akses Selamanya</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Feature 3: Latihan Rutin -->
<div class="bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container p-xl rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant md:col-span-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="edit_note">edit_note</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md mb-xs">Latihan Rutin</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md">Tugas harian dan mingguan untuk memastikan pemahaman materi tetap terjaga dan terukur.</p>
</div>
<!-- Feature 4: Progress Tracking -->
<div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white p-xl rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-lg">
<div class="flex-1 space-y-sm">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md">Evaluasi Bertahap</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Laporan perkembangan belajar dikirimkan secara berkala agar target pembelajaran Anda tetap amanah dan terukur.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full space-y-md">
<div class="h-2 w-full bg-surface-container-high rounded-full overflow-hidden">
<div class="h-full bg-tertiary-fixed-dim w-3/4"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">
<span class="">Materi Selesai</span>
<span class="">75%</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Target Peserta Section -->
<section class="bg-surface-container-high rounded-3xl p-xl mb-xl">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center space-y-md">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary">Siapa yang Cocok Mengikuti Program Ini?</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-md text-left mt-lg">
<div class="flex gap-sm items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="person_search">person_search</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Pemula Total</h4>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Belum mengenal huruf Arab atau ingin memantapkan dasar dari awal.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-sm items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="menu_book">menu_book</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Pembelajar Mandiri</h4>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Pernah belajar namun membutuhkan struktur kurikulum yang lebih rapi.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-sm items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="schedule">schedule</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Karyawan &amp; Mahasiswa</h4>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Membutuhkan waktu belajar fleksibel di sela kesibukan harian.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-sm items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" data-icon="family_restroom">family_restroom</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Keluarga Muslim</h4>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Ingin membangun lingkungan belajar bahasa Al-Qur'an di rumah.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="text-center py-xl bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden relative border border-primary">
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
<svg height="100%" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100%">
<path d="M0 100 C 20 0 50 0 100 100" fill="transparent" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 space-y-md px-md">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg">Mulai Perjalanan Anda Memahami Bahasa Al-Qur'an</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">Bergabunglah dengan ribuan santri yang telah belajar secara bertahap bersama TSL. Pendaftaran Batch baru terbatas!</p>
<div class="pt-sm">
<button class="bg-[#ea580c] text-white px-xl py-lg rounded-full font-title-lg text-title-lg shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform active:scale-95">Daftar Kelas Bahasa Arab</button>
<p class="font-label-sm text-label-sm mt-md opacity-80 italic">Amanah &amp; Terarah. Mulai langkah pertama Anda hari ini.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</main>
</Layout>
